name: Export order in Hand
query:
SELECT 
  po.supplier_name AS 'Name Of the Party',
  po.name AS 'P.O.No',
  po.transaction_date AS 'P.O.Date',
  po.total AS 'P.O.Amount(FC)',
  po.terms AS 'Terms',
  po.conversion_rate AS 'Exchange Rate',
  po.currency AS 'Currency',
  po.base_net_total AS 'Amount Rs.'
FROM `tabPurchase Order` po
LEFT JOIN `tabPurchase Invoice` pi ON po.name = pi.custom_purchase_order
WHERE po.currency != 'INR' 
  AND pi.name IS NULL
  AND (
    (%(from_date)s IS NULL AND %(to_date)s IS NULL) 
    OR (po.transaction_date BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)s)  
  )
  AND po.company = %(company)s
;

name: Export order in Hand2
query:
SELECT 
  po.supplier_name AS 'Name Of the Party',
  po.name AS 'P.O.No',
  po.transaction_date AS 'P.O.Date',
  po.total AS 'P.O.Amount(FC)',
  '10.00' as 'Freight',
  '650.00' as 'Insurance',
  po.payment_terms_template AS 'Terms',
  (
    SELECT 
      exchange_rate
    FROM `tabCurrency Exchange`
    WHERE from_currency = po.currency
      AND date = po.transaction_date
    LIMIT 1
  ) AS 'Exchange Rate',
  po.currency AS 'Currency',
  po.base_net_total AS 'Amount Rs.'
FROM `tabPurchase Order` po
LEFT JOIN `tabPurchase Invoice` pi ON po.name = pi.custom_purchase_order
WHERE po.currency != 'INR' 
  AND pi.name IS NULL
  AND (
    (%(from_date)s IS NULL AND %(to_date)s IS NULL) 
    OR (po.transaction_date BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)s)  
  );

name: HSN Wise Summary of Outward Supplies Detailed
query:
SELECT
    si_item.gst_hsn_code,
    gst_uom_map.gst_uom AS uqc,
    SUM(si_item.stock_qty) AS stock_qty,
    SUM(si_item.taxable_value) AS taxable_value,
    si_item.parent,
    si_item.item_code,
    MAX(hsn.description) AS description
FROM
    `tabSales Invoice` si
Inner JOIN
    `tabSales Invoice Item` si_item ON si.name = si_item.parent
INNER JOIN
    `tabGST HSN Code` hsn ON si_item.gst_hsn_code = hsn.name
LEFT JOIN
    `tabGST UOM Map` gst_uom_map ON si_item.stock_uom = gst_uom_map.uom
WHERE
    si.docstatus = 1
    AND si.company_gstin != IFNULL(si.billing_address_gstin, '')
GROUP BY
    si_item.parent,
    si_item.item_code,
    si_item.stock_uom;
report_name: HSN Wise Summary of Outward Supplies Detailed

name: HSN Wise Summary of Inward Supplies Detailed
query:
SELECT
    NULL AS Type_Cd,
    pi.name AS Invoice_Number,
    pi.posting_date AS Invoice_Date,
    piuom.gst_hsn_code AS HSN,
    i.item_group AS Make,
    gst_uom_map.uqc AS UQC,
    piuom.item_name AS Item_Name,
    piuom.qty AS Qty,
    piuom.rate AS Rate,
    piuom.amount AS Amount,
    pi.currency AS Currency,
    NULL AS Bond_Rebate,
    pi.total AS Basic_Value,
    NULL AS Other_Charge,
    NULL AS Bill_Value,
    pi.total AS Taxable_Value,
    
    CASE
        WHEN pi.tax_category = 'Out-State' THEN ptc.base_tax_amount
        ELSE NULL
    END AS IGST,
    CASE
        WHEN pi.tax_category = 'In-State' THEN ptc.base_tax_amount
        ELSE NULL
    END AS CGST,
    CASE
        WHEN pi.tax_category = 'In-State' THEN ptc.base_tax_amount
        ELSE NULL
    END AS SGST,
    
    CASE
        WHEN pi.disable_rounded_total = 1 THEN pi.grand_total
        ELSE pi.rounded_total
    END AS Inv_Value,
    
    SUM(ptc.rate) AS GST_total
    
FROM
    `tabPurchase Invoice Item` piuom
JOIN
    `tabPurchase Invoice` pi ON piuom.parent = pi.name
LEFT JOIN
    `tabPurchase Taxes and Charges` ptc ON pi.name = ptc.parent
LEFT JOIN
    `tabItem` i ON piuom.item_code = i.item_code
LEFT JOIN
    (SELECT
        parent,
        uom,
        gst_uom AS uqc
    FROM
        `tabGST UOM Map`) gst_uom_map ON piuom.uom = gst_uom_map.uom
WHERE
    pi.docstatus = 1 AND piuom.gst_hsn_code != ""
GROUP BY
    pi.name,
    pi.posting_date,
    piuom.gst_hsn_code,
    i.item_group,
    gst_uom_map.uqc,
    piuom.item_name,
    piuom.qty,
    piuom.rate,
    piuom.amount,
    pi.currency,
    pi.total,
    pi.tax_category,
    pi.disable_rounded_total;
report_name: HSN Wise Summary of Inward Supplies Detailed

name: Bill Purchase Register Report
query:
SELECT
    P.name AS 'ID',
    P.date AS 'Date',
    P.bank_account AS 'Bank Account',
    P.customer AS 'Customer',
    P.amount AS 'Amount',
    P.no AS 'No',
    P.spread AS 'Spread Percentage',
    P.subsequent AS 'Subsequent Percentage',
    P.interest AS 'Interest Percentage',
    P.total AS 'Total',
    P.currency AS 'Currency',
    P.amount_in_currency AS 'Amount in Currency',
    P.exchange_rate AS 'Total Exchange rate',
    PC.invoice_number AS 'Invoice Number ',
    PC.invoice_due_date AS 'Invoice Due Date ',
    PC.exchange_rate AS 'Exchange Rate '
FROM
    `tabBill Purchase` AS P
LEFT JOIN
    `tabBill Purchase Child` AS PC ON P.name = PC.parent
WHERE
    P.docstatus = 1;
